n<br />\n難到你覺得過去嘅生活會比將來好咩？"},{"pid":"2a4df6eed1481d98bdafe5af254f8c4ff9a8dd10","tid":167063,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T15:43:29.000Z","msg":"樓主， 你根本唔應該開哩個po..."},{"pid":"3ac751a09717ea151524258cbae310803d62c1cd","tid":167063,"uid":92963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T15:44:08.000Z","msg":"個世界好陌生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b827ecd177a1e84a12bff702503c4ebd0d532c37","tid":167063,"uid":39443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T15:53:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個世界好陌生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n慢慢會習慣 開頭我發現身邊嘅人全部都老哂 變哂 世界唔同左好多 好多事都以前未發生過 我都唔知點樣識應 但後來好彩有幾個時空旅行者幫我 渡過難關 <br />\n我會支持你 加油"},{"pid":"e732c446b0010ee3559f983579c5539300c6c379","tid":167063,"uid":39443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T15:54:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主， 你根本唔應該開哩個po...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都冇貪污 我只係唔小心去左未來咋嘛！"},{"pid":"523fc412511fcd2b2faf8535ae3394f7f73766a0","tid":167063,"uid":42255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T15:55:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4fd2657d53808aba98f893395ceb02cade71370d","tid":167063,"uid":92419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T15:58:33.000Z","msg":"得左<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n未來我地都冇票係手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e54455c62067178df631b7fdec0cf0172771298","tid":167063,"uid":5261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T16:09:05.000Z","msg":"我見到薯片做特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fad946e353919b15299f7bbb624334f135adaaa","tid":167063,"uid":39443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T16:12:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頂呀 頭先叫兩個細佬試 佢地宜家變左呀伯 點同佢地相處呀 樓主要負責呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能係時空警察嘅懲罰 一定有風險架啦 <br />\n由其呢幾個鐘 你地大量 穿越時空 佢地發現啦死啦今次 <br />\n大家不如避一避風頭先 怕再有意外發生"},{"pid":"dd6f50646bd508956dd0b44dff7deefeb3e3f30f","tid":167063,"uid":88642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T16:13:43.000Z","msg":"樓主....有無方法轉返返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身assignment deadline仲有六個鐘，學你咁轉一轉，過L左deadline吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317426e5706ee6a4aaeb2ad8b50201099f66dfe1","tid":167063,"uid":58583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T16:15:13.000Z","msg":"轉左5分鍾望一望 真係去左 12:05 屌"},{"pid":"54bc01c5e4de91344de51478078a751d58c752d3","tid":167063,"uid":39443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T17:17:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主....有無方法轉返返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身assignment deadline仲有六個鐘，學你咁轉一轉，過L左deadline吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n過左去就由佢啦 或者再轉 轉到唔洗交"},{"pid":"7dddcc461a093ddcd4a468802ec617d52828e89f","tid":167063,"uid":39443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T17:17:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>轉左5分鍾望一望 真係去左 12:05 屌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n珍珠都冇咁真"},{"pid":"5acf69a71f9c8521b05703425920c798a14e5544","tid":167063,"uid":93730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T17:52:17.000Z","msg":"你唔講埋點返黎我唔敢試😣"},{"pid":"8f8b8b44651abd935c7d1d6350e468897e6e87fb","tid":167063,"uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T23:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}